All Implemented Interfaces:
Servlet2Compatible, AssetLocator
public class JarServlet2Locator
extends AbstractAssetLocator
implements Servlet2Compatible

Servlet 2.x compatible locator for assets that use jar as a location key.

This locator will be automatically selected if the Servlet 2.x API is being used. See Context.initAssetLocators().

Since:
0.10.0
